Monta Ellis (born October 26, 1985) is and American Professional basketball player at the Point Guard position for the Dallas Mavericks. He wears the #8 on his jersey, and was a 2010 All-Star Canidate (did not make it on the All Star Team).

High School[]

Ellis attended Lanier High School in Jackson, Mississippi and did not attend college.

NBA Teams Played on[]

1. Golden State Warrions

2. Milwaukee Bucks

3. Dallas Mavericks
